data.description: Beautiful custom designed home with fiber internet located on 4.5 secluded acres in the highly desired Pike Co School District. This home has a new roof just installed this week. The master suite is located on the main floor with his/her closets and large dual tiled walk in shower.  The spacious kitchen is open to the family room with a built in commercial style fridge/freezer and granite tiled countertops. Also on the main floor are 2 additional large bedrooms with private vanities and a full size bath.  Just off the family room is a covered deck perfect for enjoying the outdoors and wildlife.  The basement is very spacious and perfect for entertaining or a private in-law suite with a media room or second living room, full bath, bedroom, workroom, storage room and garage with a private patio just off the bedroom. You are sure to enjoy the beautifully landscaped backyard relaxing in the large 27' above ground pool and deck area. In the backyard you will find a fire pit to enjoy those cool evenings and a spot perfect for gardening.  There is a large metal carport/work area and a chicken coop also located on the property. This home has approx 3482 finished sq ft. You will not be disappointed when you drive in from the long driveway through the wooded canopy.
